# .gitignore Template

## Purpose

Exclude files from Git version control - build artifacts, dependencies, secrets, and OS/editor files.

## Official Documentation

- [Git - gitignore](https://git-scm.com/docs/gitignore) - Pattern syntax
- [GitHub gitignore templates](https://github.com/github/gitignore) - Community templates

## When to Use

- ✅ Any Git repository
- ✅ Required for every project

## When NOT to Use

- ❌ Never skip this file
- ❌ Non-git version control (use their equivalent)

## Required Marker Files

- `.git/` directory (any git repo)

